      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no scratches or dents, while the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with all original components functioning like new. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a truly exceptional, investment-grade example of this model.",
