    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle presents a distinguished opportunity for the discerning motorist. Characterized by its robust mechanical integrity and a refined aesthetic, the automobile has been preserved to ensure consistent performance and longevity. With a comprehensive service history and a sophisticated interior, this model offers an exceptional balance of reliability and prestige. We invite serious inquiries to experience this exemplary standard of automotive engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for its next adventure! I\u2019ve taken great care of it over the years, so it\u2019s running smooth and looking sharp. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you're going to love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2-generation Carrera features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six, delivering 320hp through a crisp 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox. The powerplant utilizes VarioCam Plus valve timing and lift control for a linear power band and exceptional throttle response. The chassis remains composed via a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry, currently fitted with Bilstein dampers for improved transient handling. Crucially, this example has undergone an IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement, mitigating common catastrophic failure points. A mechanically sound, driver-spec 911 with optimal power-to-weight and minimal parasitic driveline loss.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Reliable daily driver. Well-maintained mechanicals. Clean interior. Minor exterior wear. Runs smooth.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking mechanical reliability and a well-cared-for aesthetic. The exterior finish retains a high gloss, though close inspection reveals minor road-derived stone chips on the hood and a small, superficial scratch near the trunk lid. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; the engine pulls strongly through all gears, and the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable. We have recently completed a full fluid service and installed a new set of premium all-season tires. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free. The leather seats show light, natural wear on the entry bolsters but remain soft and supportive with no rips or thinning. Every feature, from the heated seats to the premium sound system and navigation, has been tested and is fully operational. This car has been garage-kept and comes with a documented service history, proving it has been maintained to a high standard despite its minor cosmetic character marks.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver seeking an optimal balance of performance and proven reliability. Maintained to high standards, the automobile exhibits strong mechanical integrity and a sophisticated aesthetic presence. It serves as a testament to quality engineering, offering a refined driving experience that justifies its standing as a superior choice in its class. We invite professional inquiries to facilitate a comprehensive inspection of this distinguished asset.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it is looking for a brand new home! This car has been super reliable and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who needs a dependable set of wheels for daily commutes or weekend trips. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready to hit the road for many more adventures with you. If you're looking for a great, honest car that won't let you down, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996-generation Carrera 4S features the iconic wide-body silhouette and high-performance braking system derived from the Turbo. The 3.6L M96 flat-six engine utilizes VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing across the rev range, paired with a tactile six-speed manual transaxle. Mechanical highlights include a preemptive IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced clutch assembly to ensure drivetrain longevity. The all-wheel-drive system provides superior lateral grip, while the suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. A mechanically sorted example, this 911 offers the visceral feedback and analog engagement sought by discerning enthusiasts.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
